  "page_faq_title": "FAQ",
  "page_faq_subtitle": "Everything you need to know about KRAM.UA",
  "faq_q1": "How to place a bid?",
  "faq_a1": "Go to the lot page, enter your bid amount (higher than current) and click \"Place Bid\". You can also enable auto-bid — the system will automatically outbid competitors up to your maximum amount.",
  "faq_q2": "What is anti-sniping?",
  "faq_a2": "Anti-sniping is a system that adds 2 minutes to the auction end time if a bid is placed in the last minute. This gives other participants a chance to respond and makes the auction fair.",
  "faq_q3": "How to pay for a won lot?",
  "faq_a3": "After winning the auction, go to the \"Purchases\" section in your cabinet. Click \"Pay\" — available methods: LiqPay (card), Monobank transfer. After payment, the seller receives a notification and ships the item.",
  "faq_q4": "How to become a seller?",
  "faq_a4": "Register, go to your Cabinet and click \"Create Lot\". Add photos, description, choose sale type (auction / fixed price), specify delivery options. The lot appears in the catalog immediately after publishing.",
  "faq_q5": "Is there a selling commission?",
  "faq_a5": "Currently the platform operates commission-free. We are in beta testing — all deals are free. A minimal commission on successful sales may be introduced in the future.",
  "faq_q6": "How does delivery work?",
  "faq_a6": "The seller specifies available delivery options: Nova Poshta, Ukrposhta, or pickup. The buyer chooses a convenient option when ordering. After shipping, you receive a tracking number in the \"Purchases\" section.",
  "faq_q7": "What if the item doesn't match the description?",
  "faq_a7": "Contact the seller via the built-in chat. If you can't resolve it — reach out to support via the Contacts page. We'll help sort it out.",

  "page_about_title": "About Us",
  "page_about_subtitle": "KRAM.UA is a Ukrainian online auction platform where anyone can sell unwanted items or find a great deal.",
  "about_mission_title": "🔨 Our Mission",
  "about_mission_text": "To create a transparent, safe and convenient marketplace for trading in Ukraine. We believe every item deserves a second chance, and every buyer — a fair price.",
  "about_why_title": "⚡ Why Us?",
  "about_why_1": "<strong>Real auctions from 1 UAH.</strong> No markups — real people, real bids.",
  "about_why_2": "<strong>Anti-sniping.</strong> A bid in the last minute extends the auction by 2 minutes. Fair play for everyone.",
  "about_why_3": "<strong>Seller ratings.</strong> Every seller has a public rating and reviews — you always know who you're dealing with.",
  "about_why_4": "<strong>Built-in chat.</strong> Talk to sellers or buyers directly on the platform.",
  "about_why_5": "<strong>No commission.</strong> The platform is in beta — all deals are free.",
  "about_security_title": "🛡️ Security",
  "about_security_text": "We use modern encryption protocols (JWT, helmet, rate-limiting) to protect your data. Passwords are stored hashed. Payment operations are processed through trusted services like LiqPay.",
  "about_roadmap_title": "🚀 Roadmap",
  "about_roadmap_text": "We are actively working on new features: mobile app, advanced seller analytics, postal service integration for automatic delivery tracking, and a seller verification program.",

