  "security_chat_title": "Contact Chat Moderation",
  "security_chat_1": "The KRAM.UA built-in chat automatically hides phone numbers, email addresses, and links to external messengers until the deal is confirmed.",
  "security_chat_2": "<strong>Why this matters:</strong> scammers often try to move conversations off-platform to avoid oversight. All negotiations, delivery terms, and payments must happen exclusively in the built-in chat.",
